me pits klutziness against good intentions – a ticking clock against wilting houseplants. Move into Nora’s cozy-but-cluttered witch’s cottage, brew more than 50 powerful potions and achieve domestic bliss in this truly magical visual novel / time management hybrid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/a4481b7f2a5e7f2a047018358717a0dc.avif?t=1757700785\" width=800 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/4b46fc7221d2562340df0e7618121fb7.poster.avif?t=1757700785\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/4b46fc7221d2562340df0e7618121fb7.webm?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/4b46fc7221d2562340df0e7618121fb7.mp4?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your adventure, you are sure to meet many interesting and truly intriguing characters. Take your time to chat with them all and immerse yourself deeper into the magical world of spells, potions and fun. Who knows, maybe some of them will become your friends?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/bb9159d8b5ce550dcc9fbb75dd90a6ab.avif?t=1757700785\" width=800 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Brew potions and fulfill orders</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Grow and harvest alchemical plants… or sell them for money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Decorate and upgrade rooms of your hut</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Hone and upgrade your abilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Collect more than 20 unique ingredients</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Enjoy the cozy and relaxing nature of the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
